  "detailed_description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2115040/extras/dbb97c4a70a44e54f1320b8e79b8a338.avif?t=1755676843\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2115040/extras_big/dbb97c4a70a44e54f1320b8e79b8a338.avif?t=1755676843 width=800 height=153 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Spooky Survivors</strong> is a fast-paced rogue lite meets survivor like that combines humor, strategy, and supernatural chaos. Play as Van Hobo, an eccentric monster hunter with a knack for survival, as you battle relentless hordes of ghastly foes in a haunted realm.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2115040/extras/64ca88d13dcc374e4ef95cf52a8136f2.webp?t=1755676843\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2115040/extras_big/64ca88d13dcc374e4ef95cf52a8136f2.webp?t=1755676843 width=800 height=40 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2115040/extras/e63e5f605adc6ee0b158e0a4aa1ffb47.poster.avif?t=1755676843\" width=600 height=200 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2115040/extras/e63e5f605adc6ee0b158e0a4aa1ffb47.webm?t=1755676843\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2115040/extras/e63e5f605adc6ee0b158e0a4aa1ffb47.mp4?t=1755676843\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >  <span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2115040/extras/64ca88d13dcc374e4ef95cf52a8136f2.webp?t=1755676843\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2115040/extras_big/64ca88d13dcc374e4ef95cf52a8136f2.webp?t=1755676843 width=800 height=40 /></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Features:</h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>All Unlocks from the Start</strong>: Begin with every upgrade at your fingertips, but the power is in your choices—level up strategically to adapt to the chaos.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Pray To The Celestials: </strong>Collect prayer crystals and trade them in for special attacks or buffs like meteor strikes or double damage! </p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>All hand drawn:</strong> Everything you see in game is hand drawn with love and care creating a unique looking and feeling experience!</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Face off against Godlike bosses:</strong> As if the normal spookies weren't bad enough, you'll have to contend with bosses too!</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Dynamic Challenges</strong>: Face evolving waves of enemies that test your strategy and reflexes.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Procedural Variety</strong>: No two runs are the same, with randomized  enemies and levels keeping the challenge fresh.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Quirky Humor</strong>: Embrace the light-hearted charm of Van Hobo as you flip the script on traditional monster hunting.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Chase Glory</strong>: Push yourself run after run, wave after wave, and fight to secure your spot in the top 100 leaderboard!</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2115040/extras/64ca88d13dcc374e4ef95cf52a8136f2.webp?t=1755676843\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2115040/extras_big/64ca88d13dcc374e4ef95cf52a8136f2.webp?t=1755676843 width=800 height=40 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2115040/extras/5813de90bfe9fe636ec694c0a2aea87a.poster.avif?t=1755676843\" width=600 height=340 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2115040/extras/5813de90bfe9fe636ec694c0a2aea87a.webm?t=1755676843\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2115040/extras/5813de90bfe9fe636ec694c0a2aea87a.mp4?t=1755676843\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2115040/extras/64ca88d13dcc374e4ef95cf52a8136f2.webp?t=1755676843\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2115040/extras_big/64ca88d13dcc374e4ef95cf52a8136f2.webp?t=1755676843 width=800 height=40 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2115040/extras/605c7b484f58b855689332640f540589.poster.avif?t=1755676843\" width=600 height=200 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2115040/extras/605c7b484f58b855689332640f540589.webm?t=1755676843\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2115040/extras/605c7b484f58b855689332640f540589.mp4?t=1755676843\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2115040/extras/64ca88d13dcc374e4ef95cf52a8136f2.webp?t=1755676843\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2115040/extras_big/64ca88d13dcc374e4ef95cf52a8136f2.webp?t=1755676843 width=800 height=40 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p>",
  "about_the_game": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2115040/extras/dbb97c4a70a44e54f1320b8e79b8a338.avif?t=1755676843\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2115040/extras_big/dbb97c4a70a44e54f1320b8e79b8a338.avif?t=1755676843 width=800 height=153 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Spooky Survivors</strong> is a fast-paced rogue lite meets survivor like that combines humor, strategy, and supernatural chaos. Play as Van Hobo, an eccentric monster hunter with a knack for survival, as you battle relentless hordes of ghastly foes in a haunted realm.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2115040/extras/64ca88d13dcc374e4ef95cf52a8136f2.webp?t=1755676843\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2115040/extras_big/64ca88d13dcc374e4ef95cf52a8136f2.webp?t=1755676843 width=800 height=40 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2115040/extras/e63e5f605adc6ee0b158e0a4aa1ffb47.poster.avif?t=1755676843\" width=600 height=200 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2115040/extras/e63e5f605adc6ee0b158e0a4aa1ffb47.webm?t=1755676843\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2115040/extras/e63e5f605adc6ee0b158e0a4aa1ffb47.mp4?t=1755676843\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >  <span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2115040/extras/64ca88d13dcc374e4ef95cf52a8136f2.webp?t=1755676843\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2115040/extras_big/64ca88d13dcc374e4ef95cf52a8136f2.webp?t=1755676843 width=800 height=40 /></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Features:</h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>All Unlocks from the Start</strong>: Begin with every upgrade at your fingertips, but the power is in your choices—level up strategically to adapt to the chaos.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Pray To The Celestials: </strong>Collect prayer crystals and trade them in for special attacks or buffs like meteor strikes or double damage! </p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>All hand drawn:</strong> Everything you see in game is hand drawn with love and care creating a unique looking and feeling experience!</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Face off against Godlike bosses:</strong> As if the normal spookies weren't bad enough, you'll have to contend with bosses too!</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Dynamic Challenges</strong>: Face evolving waves of enemies that test your strategy and reflexes.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Procedural Variety</strong>: No two runs are the same, with randomized  enemies and levels keeping the challenge fresh.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Quirky Humor</strong>: Embrace the light-hearted charm of Van Hobo as you flip the script on traditional monster hunting.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Chase Glory</strong>: Push yourself run after run, wave after wave, and fight to secure your spot in the top 100 leaderboard!</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2115040/extras/64ca88d13dcc374e4ef95cf52a8136f2.webp?t=1755676843\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2115040/extras_big/64ca88d13dcc374e4ef95cf52a8136f2.webp?t=1755676843 width=800 height=40 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2115040/extras/5813de90bfe9fe636ec694c0a2aea87a.poster.avif?t=1755676843\" width=600 height=340 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2115040/extras/5813de90bfe9fe636ec694c0a2aea87a.webm?t=1755676843\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2115040/extras/5813de90bfe9fe636ec694c0a2aea87a.mp4?t=1755676843\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2115040/extras/64ca88d13dcc374e4ef95cf52a8136f2.webp?t=1755676843\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2115040/extras_big/64ca88d13dcc374e4ef95cf52a8136f2.webp?t=1755676843 width=800 height=40 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2115040/extras/605c7b484f58b855689332640f540589.poster.avif?t=1755676843\" width=600 height=200 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2115040/extras/605c7b484f58b855689332640f540589.webm?t=1755676843\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2115040/extras/605c7b484f58b855689332640f540589.mp4?t=1755676843\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2115040/extras/64ca88d13dcc374e4ef95cf52a8136f2.webp?t=1755676843\" data-big-src=https://shared.akam